    • GasPlanet

      public GasPlanet(String name, double mass, double diameter, double averageTemperature, String surfaceType, boolean hasLiquidWater, String gasComposition, String coreComposition, double radiationLevel)
      Constructor for objects of class gas Planet
      Parameters:
      name - Name of the planet, max 30 chars
      mass - mass of the planet, measured in ronnagrams earth is approx 6.0rg must be > 0.1 default to 0.1
      diameter - diameter of the planet, measured in kilometres must be > 0.5 default to 0.5
      averageTemperature - Average temperatur of the planet, Average surface temperature in °C must be a value between -400 and 400 default 0
      surfaceType - surface type of the planet, e.g., “rocky”, “volcanic”, “metallic” max 20 chars
      hasLiquidWater - if the planet has liquid water,true or false
      gasComposition - gas planet compositon, max 20 chars
      coreComposition - Must be one of Rocky and Metallic, Proportionally Small, Liquid Metallic Hydrogen Compressed Hydrogen or Ice Giant default UNKNOWN can use CoreCompositionUtility class
      radiationLevel - Higher in gas giant min .01 max 200.05 default .9
